@prefix ex: <http://example.org/disjunction-branching#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

ex:Seed a owl:Class .
ex:Left a owl:Class .
ex:Right a owl:Class .
ex:Resolved a owl:Class .

ex:Seed rdfs:subClassOf [
    a owl:Class ;
    owl:unionOf ( ex:Left ex:Right )
] .

ex:Left owl:disjointWith ex:Right .
ex:Right rdfs:subClassOf ex:Resolved .
